---
description: FastAPI folder structure
globs:
  - "backend/app/**/*.*"
alwaysApply: false
---
- `backend/app/main.py`: app entrypoint and wiring.
- `backend/app/routers/`: API routes.
- `backend/app/schemas/`: Pydantic request/response schemas.
- `backend/app/models/`: database models.
- `backend/app/services/`: business logic.
- `backend/app/dependencies/`: shared dependencies.
- Keep routers thin and move business logic into services.
